<br>
Pre-casting: never heard this idea before.  Would be cool but probably too much of a change in Verant's game engine for them to bother implementing such a thing.<br>
<br>
Mana Control:  maybe.  But only if Verant suddenly changes their position that we need more mana regen then everyone else.<br>
<br>
Mana Protection:  are you suggesting drawing mana from both PCs and NPCs?  Such a power could be a source of abuse...VI would probably be pretty resistant to such an idea.<br>
<br>
Flight: Yes.  I understand we COULD fly in Beta using levitation.  Wish we had it again if only for the pure fun of it.<br>
<br>
Magically Inclined: interesting idea.  Gives added incentive for us to get resistance gear.  Would be interesting to see how wizards would react to actually having to SEEK getting nuked at. hmmmm....<br>
<br>
-- Lim'Dul<br>
